# Context Checkpoints Directory

This directory stores conversation state checkpoints for efficient chat resets.

## Usage

Create checkpoint:
  perl scripts/export-context-checkpoint.pl [--session-name=NAME]

List checkpoints:
  perl scripts/load-context-checkpoint.pl --list

Load checkpoint:
  perl scripts/load-context-checkpoint.pl [--session-name=NAME]

## Purpose

Checkpoints allow resetting chat context while preserving essential state,
reducing token baseline by 80-90% for continued work.
